xmpp-share-server 0.8.0 (UNRELEASED)
 * start using shared libraries.
 * expose incoming client statistics.

xmpp-share-server 0.7.7 (2012-01-23)
  * share_client: split share client into its process.

xmpp-share-server 0.7.6 (2011-10-08)
 * QXmppServer: add initial multithreading.

xmpp-share-server 0.7.5 (2011-10-06)
 * QXmppServer: make it possible to reload some settings.
 * QXmppServer: improve client routing scalability.

xmpp-share-server 0.7.4 (2011-09-31)
 * mod_http: allow cross-domain requests on static files.

xmpp-share-server 0.7.3 (2011-09-30)
 * mod_http: add support for serving static files.

xmpp-share-server 0.7.2 (2011-07-20)
 * mod_archive: add support for collection removal.
 * mod_http: add request / response logging.

xmpp-share-server 0.7.1 (2011-06-28)
 * Update QXmpp to catch errors on outgoing S2S connections.
 * mod_share: report total size for share clients.

xmpp-share-server 0.7.0 (2011-02-23)
 * Update QXmpp to fix server-to-server dialback support.
 * mod_archive: add a module for message archiving and offline messages.
 * mod_bosh: add a module for Bidirectional-streams Over Synchronous HTTP.
 * mod_muc: add a module for multi-user chat.
 * mod_private: add a module for private XML storage.
 * mod_proxy65: improve logging and transfer termination.
 * mod_roster: correct local-to-local subscription requests.

xmpp-share-server 0.6.4 (2010-11-08)
 * Add finer control over the log level.
 * mod_diag: add a module for diagnostics reporting.

xmpp-share-server 0.6.3 (2010-09-29)
 * Use new URL for authentication.
 * Send a user agent when performing authentication.

xmpp-share-server 0.6.2 (2010-09-14)
 * Update QXmpp to correctly handle presence elements with multiple extensions.
 * Update QXmpp to fix combined prefix + filter share searches.
 * Make it possible to specify the log level in the configuration file.
 * mod_share: add timeout for forwarded search requests.

xmpp-share-server 0.6.0 (2010-09-01)
 * Use QXmppServer as provided by QXmpp.
 * mod_share: give peers a minute before exploring them.
 * mod_share: re-explore peers every 3 hours.
 * mod_proxy65: add statistics for files/bytes transfered per hour.

xmpp-share-server 0.5.3 (2010-08-18)
 * Add support for certificate chains.

xmpp-share-server 0.5.2 (2010-07-26)
 * Update QDjango to fix memory leak in database connection.

xmpp-share-server 0.5.0 (2010-07-26)
 * Update QXmpp to fix potential crashes.
 * Add a sleep to make "restart" on init script work.
 * Add proper authentication.

xmpp-share-server 0.4.3 (2010-06-15)
 * Fix discovery response IQ type so share server discovery always works.
 * Display total share size in the share peer list.
 * List share peers by decreasing share size.
 * Report number of available bytes and files in statistics.

xmpp-share-server 0.4.2 (2010-05-31)
 * Report maximum / minimum / average transfer speeds in statistics.

xmpp-share-server 0.4.1 (2010-05-25)
 * Update QDjango to avoid double SQL query execution.
 * Make it possible to pass a host name for SOCKS5 server.

xmpp-share-server 0.4.0 (2010-05-21)
 * Add xmpp-share-client.

xmpp-share-server 0.3.2 (2010-05-18)
 * Report version in statistics.

xmpp-share-server 0.3.1 (2010-05-12)
 * Add support for statistics.
